      div.panel-heading
        | Substution
      div.panel-body
        | Sometimes values from the request need to be inserted into the response.
        br
        | To faciliate this there is a macro format that can be used to retrieve and replace
        | the necessary values from the request
        pre
          #&lt;location&gt;:&lt;key|search&gt;:[&lt;encoding&gt;,...]
        ul
          li| location - single character value to source the key from
            ul
              li| h - headers
              li| c - cookies
              li| s - scheme (protocol)
              li| d - domain (host)
              li| p - url path
              li| q - query string
              li| b - request body
          li| key|search - a string (or regular expresion) for matching against fields when looking through the location
          li| encoding - a comma delimited list of encoding types
            ul
              li| json - value will be json encoded
              li| % - value will be 'percent encoded' (urlencode)